==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: fussbudget
<hw>fuss"budg*et</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a person who thinks excessively
about unfortunate things that might happen; one who is excessively
concerned about matters of trifling importance.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> worrier, fusspot, worrywart.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>fussbudgety</ent>⟦br⟧
